00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:45,218
Not everything buried beneath Kerning City is monstrous. Some of it... is simply lost. Jake found a hat left behind on the railway and set in motion a mystery that wound its way to Naora Hospital... where a woman named Jane Doe was recovering from surgery and asking passersby to help her find Shades. She wanted a bronze mirror... to see how her operation had come out... a request that seemed ordinary until you stood in the subway's flickering light... and realized the question she was REALLY asking. The boundary between the living and the dead in this city is not a wall. It is a smudge.
